      <title>Tiny Video Studio 的中世纪游戏给波兰工业带来希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/medieval-game-by-tiny-video-studio-gives-hope-to-polish-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰一家小型独立工作室本周末发布的《庄园领主》电子游戏销量已超过百万份，及时推动了该国的电脑娱乐产业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/medieval-game-by-tiny-video-studio-gives-hope-to-polish-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 12:18:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果竞争对手重组以挑战 iPhone 和 Vision Pro</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-04-28/apple-rivals-retool-to-compete-with-iphone-and-vision-pro-ios-18-and-ai-details-lvjhucsv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果的主要竞争对手正在调整其智能手机和耳机战略，这表明他们嗅到了机遇。另外：新款iPad Pro将迎来苹果向AI硬件的转变； iOS 18 和公司人工智能计划的新细节浮出水面； Vision Pro 的首席营销人员退休了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-04-28/apple-rivals-retool-to-compete-with-iphone-and-vision-pro-ios-18-and-ai-details-lvjhucsv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 12:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克出人意料地访华，寻求特斯拉营收增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司(Tesla Inc.)的埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)周日未经宣布访问中国，寻求驾驶辅助软件的批准，以帮助遏制该汽车制造商的收入下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透社称马斯克前往北京讨论全自动驾驶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-heads-to-beijing-to-discuss-full-self-driving-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社援引两位不愿透露姓名的知情人士的话报道，特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)将前往北京会见中国高级官员，并讨论在中国推出全自动驾驶软件的事宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-heads-to-beijing-to-discuss-full-self-driving-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 05:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电信巨头因移动困境加剧而感到痛苦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/telecom-tycoons-feel-pain-from-rising-mobile-woes-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在债务成本几乎为零的情况下通过推出无线网络积累财富的亿万富翁们发现，他们的财富因借贷成本上升以及基金经理对该行业前景的谨慎而受到挤压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/telecom-tycoons-feel-pain-from-rising-mobile-woes-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
